import React from "react"
import * as Mui from "@mui/material"
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"

function Navbar() {
    return(
        <Mui.Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', textAlign: 'center'}}>
            <Link to="">
                <Mui.Typography>Home</Mui.Typography>
                </Link>
            <Link to="/login">
                <Mui.Typography>Login</Mui.Typography>
                </Link>
            <Link to="/register">
                <Mui.Typography>Register</Mui.Typography>
                </Link>
            <Link to="/logout">
                <Mui.Typography>Logout</Mui.Typography>
                </Link>
        </Mui.Box>
    )

}

export default Navbar
